oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Knox County Jail site
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Thompson Brothers
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Site of new Knox County Jail. Ordered by Knox County Architect Office (Mr. Wilhort/Barker). July 8, 1935. View from Gay Street, cars parked on street. Edge of Knox County Courthouse visible at right.
